lead_paragraph: Two mushers competing in the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog race were attacked by a man who drove a snowmobile into their dog teams, on Saturday morning. One dog was killed.

headline.print_headline: Man Is Arrested Over Iditarod Crashes
headline.main: Sled Teams Attacked in Iditarod Race

snippet: Two mushers competing in the Iditarod Trail Sled Dog race were attacked by a man who drove a snowmobile into their dog teams, on Saturday morning. One dog was killed.
abstract: Arnold Demoski of Nulato, Alaska, is arrested on suspicion of intentionally driving snowmobile into two teams participating in Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race.
